headline.print_headline: France Prepares for Return to Stade de France
headline.main: France Prepares for Return to Stade de France

snippet: France’s players are expecting an emotional evening when they return to the Stade de France for the first time since the Nov. 13 bombings at the national stadium.
lead_paragraph: France’s players are expecting an emotional evening when they return to the Stade de France for the first time since the Nov. 13 bombings at the national stadium.
